Dario Calmese bụ onye Amerịka na-ese ihe na onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke sitere na Missouri.  Ọ bụ onye Afrịka-Amerịka mbụ sere foto mkpuchi Vanity Fair. Calmese bụ onye na-elekọta podcast, Institute of Black Imagination.

Ọ malitere ise foto n'afọ 2012 mgbe ọ na-aga School of Visual Arts. Foto ya nke onye na-anakọta ejiji na Harlem bụ Lana Turner bụ akụkụ nke ihe ngosi pụrụ iche n'afọ 2015. N'afọ 2013 ọ ghọrọ onye nduzi maka ihe ngosi ejiji nke Kerby Jean-Raymond na onye nduzi
N'afọ 2019, ọ duziri ihe ngosi Pyer Moss na Kings Theater na Brooklyn. Maka mkpuchi Julaị/Ọgọọst ai 2020 nke Vanity Fair, o sere foto Viola Davis
Calmese arụwokwa ọrụ maka Vanity Fair n'oge gara aga, ọ bụ ezie na nke a bụ mkpuchi magazin mbụ ya, na mkpuchi magazin nke mbụ maka Vanity fair nke onye na-ese foto n'Afrịka-Amerịka gbara
Ọ gbagburu onye na-eme ihe nkiri Billy Porter, onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri George MacKay na onye na-ahụ maka Broadway Adrienne Warren maka magazin ahụ.
